{
  "page": "War for the dawn",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">Not to be confused with the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_for_the_Dawn\" title=\"Battle for the Dawn\">Battle for the Dawn</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background:#B0C4DE;\">War for the dawn</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Location</th><td>\nWorldwide</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table width=\"100%\" style=\"text-align:left; background:none\">\n  <tbody><tr><td width=\"50%\" colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#B0C4DE; text-align:center;\">Belligerents</td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\">Humanity</td><td style=\"border-left: 1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Others\" title=\"Others\">Others</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#B0C4DE; text-align:center;\">Notable commanders</td></tr><tr><td>The <a href=\"/index.php/Prince_that_was_promised\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Prince that was promised\">prince that was promised</a></td><td style=\"border-left: 1px dotted #aaa;\">Unknown</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#B0C4DE; text-align:center;\">Strength</td></tr><tr><td></td><td style=\"border-left: 1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Wights\" title=\"Wights\">Wights</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#B0C4DE; text-align:center;\">Losses</td></tr><tr><td></td><td style=\"border-left: 1px dotted #aaa;\">Unknown</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>war for the dawn</b><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos78.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos78.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> is a prophesied conflict.  It is said that the coming war will be a war for life itself.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos78.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos78.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>  The war for the dawn will be fought by humanity (and possibly the old races, such as the <a href=\"/index.php/Children_of_the_forest\" title=\"Children of the forest\">children of the forest</a>) against the <a href=\"/index.php/Others\" title=\"Others\">Others</a>, and according to some characters, the <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Other\" title=\"Great Other\">Great Other</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/The_prince_that_was_promised\" title=\"The prince that was promised\">The prince that was promised</a> is destined to play a part in the war for the dawn.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos78.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos78.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Thousands of years ago another war against the Others took place during the <a href=\"/index.php/Long_Night\" title=\"Long Night\">Long Night</a>. According to stories, it ended in the defeat of the Others at the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_for_the_Dawn\" title=\"Battle for the Dawn\">Battle for the Dawn</a> or through the actions of the <a href=\"/index.php/Last_hero\" title=\"Last hero\">last hero</a>/<a href=\"/index.php/Azor_Ahai\" title=\"Azor Ahai\">Azor Ahai</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=War_for_the_dawn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=War_for_the_dawn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>On <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonstone\" title=\"Dragonstone\">Dragonstone</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Melisandre\" title=\"Melisandre\">Melisandre</a> speaks of a great battle is the coming war between the <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Other\" title=\"Great Other\">Great Other</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/R%27hllor\" title=\"R&#39;hllor\">R'hllor</a>, the Lord of Light,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> which has been waged since time began.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> Melisandre states the Great Other is marshaling his power, a power fell and evil and strong beyond measure, and that the battle has begun.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>After King <a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis Baratheon</a> makes <a href=\"/index.php/Davos_Seaworth\" title=\"Davos Seaworth\">Davos Seaworth</a> the Lord of the <a href=\"/index.php/Rainwood\" title=\"Rainwood\">Rainwood</a> and his <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">Hand of the King</a>, he tells Davos that it is he whom he wants beside him for the battle. Davos thinks Stannis means another battle against the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">Lannisters</a>, but <a href=\"/index.php/Melisandre\" title=\"Melisandre\">Melisandre</a> explains to Davos that it is the great battle Stannis is speaking of. Stannis then tells Davos that he saw the great battle in the flames. Davos is astonished, as it is not like Stannis to lie about such a thing. Stannis tells him that after the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Blackwater\" title=\"Battle of the Blackwater\">Battle of the Blackwater</a> he was lost in despair but Melisandre bid him to gaze into the hearth fire; he describes to Davos what he saw in the flames,\n</p>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>The ashes were white, rising in the updraft, yet all at once it seemed as if they were falling.  Snow, I thought.  Then the sparks in the air seemed to circle, to become a ring of torches, and I was looking <b>through</b> the fire down on some <a href=\"/index.php/Fist_of_the_First_Men\" title=\"Fist of the First Men\">high hill in a forest</a>. The cinders had become <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Fist_of_the_First_Men\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Battle of the Fist of the First Men\">men in black behind the torches</a>, and there were <a href=\"/index.php/Wights\" title=\"Wights\">shapes moving through the snow</a>. For all the heat of the fire, <a href=\"/index.php/Others\" title=\"Others\">I felt a cold so terrible</a> I shivered, and when I did the sight was gone, the fire but a fire once again. But what I saw was real, I’d stake my kingdom on it.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></p></div>\n</blockquote>\n<p>After the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_beneath_the_Wall\" title=\"Battle beneath the Wall\">battle beneath the Wall</a> Melisandre states that the war they have come to fight is a war for life itself. Melisandre tells Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Aemon_Targaryen_(son_of_Maekar_I)\" title=\"Aemon Targaryen (son of Maekar I)\">Aemon</a> that <a href=\"/index.php/The_prince_that_was_promised\" title=\"The prince that was promised\">the prince that was promised</a> is standing before him, King Stannis Baratheon, who is <a href=\"/index.php/Azor_Ahai\" title=\"Azor Ahai\">Azor Ahai</a> reborn and that in him the prophecies are fulfilled.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos78.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos78.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=War_for_the_dawn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>These little wars are no more than a scuffle of children before what is to come.  The <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Other\" title=\"Great Other\">one whose name may not be spoken</a> is marshalling his power ... a power fell and evil and strong beyond measure.  Soon comes the cold, and the <a href=\"/index.php/Long_night_that_never_ends\" title=\"Long night that never ends\">night that never ends</a> ... Unless true men find the courage to fight it.  Men whose hearts are fire.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Melisandre\" title=\"Melisandre\">Melisandre</a>, to <a href=\"/index.php/Davos_Seaworth\" title=\"Davos Seaworth\">Davos Seaworth</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>It is death we choose, or life.  Darkness, or light.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Melisandre\" title=\"Melisandre\">Melisandre</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>The battle has begun ... The sand is running in the glass more quickly now, and man's hour on earth is almost done.  We must act boldly, or all hope is lost.  Westeros must unite beneath her one true king, <a href=\"/index.php/The_prince_that_was_promised\" title=\"The prince that was promised\">the prince that was promised</a>, Lord of <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonstone\" title=\"Dragonstone\">Dragonstone</a> and chosen of <a href=\"/index.php/R%27hllor\" title=\"R&#39;hllor\">R'hllor</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Melisandre\" title=\"Melisandre\">Melisandre</a>, to <a href=\"/index.php/Davos_Seaworth\" title=\"Davos Seaworth\">Davos Seaworth</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Ours is a war for life itself, and should we fail the world dies with us.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos78.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos78.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Melisandre\" title=\"Melisandre\">Melisandre</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>It is the war for the dawn you speak of, <a href=\"/index.php/Melisandre\" title=\"Melisandre\">my lady</a>. But where is <a href=\"/index.php/The_prince_that_was_promised\" title=\"The prince that was promised\">the prince that was promised</a>?<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos78.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos78.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Aemon_Targaryen_(son_of_Maekar_I)\" title=\"Aemon Targaryen (son of Maekar I)\">Aemon</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=War_for_the_dawn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos78.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos78.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos78.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos78.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos78.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos78.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\">1.4</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos78.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\">1.5</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_78\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 78\">Chapter 78</a>, Samwell V.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\">2.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\">2.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-4\">2.4</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_36\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 36\">Chapter 36</a>, Davos IV.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">3.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\">3.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_25\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 25\">Chapter 25</a>, Davos III.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403133734\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.086 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.264 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1610/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10791/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 12477/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 2478/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 4145/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.170/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 5.29 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  250.375      1 -total\n 77.18%  193.228      1 Template:Infobox_military_conflict\n 76.77%  192.218      1 Template:Infobox\n 11.64%   29.142      1 Template:Hatnote\n  9.09%   22.764     13 Template:Ref\n  5.95%   14.886     13 Template:Ref/core\n  4.21%   10.545      6 Template:Quote\n  1.06%    2.647      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:15766-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403133734 and revision id 316712\n -->\n",
